author: stefan2
msg: Make sure that txdelta cache keys use separate key spaces for packed
and non-packed revisions. Otherwise, there may be occasional collisions
if the repository is being packed after the cache has been filled with
txdelta windows from previously non-packed revisions.
(get_window_key): distinguish between packed and non-packed "file numbers"
